x4freetext: The maximum energy of the protons was 6.5 MeV. The
energy degradation was calculated according to
J.H.Smith, phys.Rev.71,32(1947).
No errors are specified. In a following paper (J.P.
Blaser et al. Helv. Phys.Acta,24,441,1951) a global
error discussion for similar experiments is contained.
